<li class="menu-item">
<img src="images/esp.jpeg" width="200" alt="Espresso" class="menu-image">
<h3 class="name">Espresso</h3>
<p class="text">A strong, concentrated coffee made by forcing hot water through finely-ground beans</p>
</li>
<li class="menu-item">
<img src="images/la.jpeg" width="200" alt="latte" class="menu-image">
<h3 class="name">Latte</h3>
<p class="text">Similar to a cappuccino but with more steamed milk and a thinner layer of foam, making it milder and creamier.</p>
</li>
<li class="menu-item">
<img src="images/capp.png" width="200" alt="Cappuccino" class="menu-image">
<h3 class="name">Cappuccino</h3>
<p class="text"> Espresso is combined with steamed milk and topped with a thick layer of milk foam, creating a creamy texture.</p>
</li>
<li class="menu-item">
<img src="images/pum1.jpeg" width="200" alt="Pumpkin spiced latte" class="menu-image">
<h3 class="name">Pumpkin spiced latte</h3>
<p class="text">A seasonal favorite featuring espresso, steamed milk, and a blend of pumpkin spice flavors like cinnamon, nutmeg, and cloves.</p>
</li>
<li class="menu-item">
<img src="images/pmocha.jpeg" width="200" alt="Peppermint Mocha" class="menu-image">
<h3 class="name">Peppermint Mocha</h3>
<p class="text"> festive coffee drink combining espresso, steamed milk, chocolate syrup, and peppermint flavoring.</p>
</li>
<li class="menu-item">
<img src="images/am.jpeg" width="200" alt="Americano" class="menu-image">
<h3 class="name">Americano</h3>
<p class="text"> Espresso diluted with hot water for a smoother taste.</p>
</li>
<li class="menu-item">
<img src="images/macc.jpeg" width="200" alt=" Macchiato" class="menu-image">
<h3 class="name"> Macchiato</h3>
<p class="text">Espresso with a small amount of milk or foam for a bold taste.</p>
</li>
<li class="menu-item">
<img src="images/ice1.jpeg" width="200" alt=" Iced Coffee" class="menu-image">
<h3 class="name"> Iced Coffee</h3>
<p class="text">Brewed coffee chilled and served over ice, sometimes with milk or syrup.</p>
</li>
<li class="menu-item">
<img src="images/brew.png" width="200" alt="Cold Brew" class="menu-image">
<h3 class="name">Cold Brew</h3>
<p class="text">Coffee steeped in cold water for several hours, ring in a smooth, less acidic drink</p>
</li>
<li class="menu-item">
<img src="images/free.png" alt="Flat White" class="menu-image">
<h3 class="name">Flat White</h3>
<p class="text">Similar to a latte but with a stronger coffee flavor and velvety microfoam</p>
</li>
</ul>
